WEBVTT

00:08:28.293 --> 00:08:31.706
but also by great
public-health storytellers

00:08:31.730 --> 00:08:34.109
with a passion for science.

00:08:34.133 --> 00:08:38.056
Regular citizens could get
accessible information

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.087
about complex technologies

00:08:40.111 --> 00:08:43.940
like artificial intelligence
or gene editing,

00:08:43.964 --> 00:08:48.503
enabling us to participate
in the policy conversations

00:08:48.527 --> 00:08:51.963
that directly impact our health and lives.

00:08:53.948 --> 00:08:55.098
Fourth,

00:08:56.095 --> 00:08:58.761
we need to get the right to go to court.

00:08:59.245 --> 00:09:02.888
Right now in America,
after a patent is granted,